# ─── Cargo / Rust build artifacts ────────────────────────────────────────
/target
**/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak
*.pdb

# ─── Editor / IDE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── OS noise ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ─── Test fixture host-specific outputs ──────────────────────────────────
# We commit `run.stdout` (the expected program output) but NOT the
# platform-specific binaries themselves, which would bloat the repo
# and only run on the OS+architecture they were built for.
tests/fixtures/expected/native/*/skot
tests/fixtures/expected/native/*/skot.ll

# ─── Per-fixture generated `build/` directories ──────────────────────────
# Multi-module Gradle projects under examples/ produce these.
**/build

# ─── cargo-dist artifact dirs ────────────────────────────────────────────
# `dist` builds release artifacts under `target/distrib/`.
target/distrib/

# ─── Local environment ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.envrc
.env
.env.local
